(33, 'Placement Cell of the Programme', NULL, 'placement-cell-of-the-it-scholarship-project', '<p><strong>The Employment Market &amp; IsDB-BISEW Graduates: </strong>The most striking aspect of the project has been its outstanding placement record. Almost all graduates of the programme get placed in jobs right after completing their training. It currently maintains 92% of placement record. These employments take place in a wide variety of sectors and firms.</p>\r\n<p>The strong hands-on skills of IsDB-BISEW graduates, their familiarity with popular and modern tools and technologies make them very attractive to ICT employers. One measure of the IT Scholarship Project\'s success is that organizations who recruit the graduates of the project once tend to make repeat recruitment\'s from the project. Their experience with graduates of the IT Scholarship Project has been very productive and thus encourages them to take more IsDB-BISEW graduates into their organizations&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Placement Assistances:</strong> The project has a cell for the placement of IsDB-BISEW Graduates. All kinds of placement assistance are provided to the Graduates. The cell maintains sound relations with the employers and contentiously works for arranging interview for the graduates.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Grooming the graduates:</strong> After training Graduates are prepared for the interview. Graduates are trained on CV writing and interview giving skills. Graduates are also briefed about career planning.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>CareerHub:</strong> Placement Cell maintains a dedicated web-based job site named CareerHub (http://careerhub.idb-bisew.info). Only the graduates of IDB-BISEW keep their CV in this site. Employers choose CVs from this site.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Employment Status:</strong> Placement Cell continuously update the employment status of graduates and keep the status available for all trainees of IsDB-BISEW so that graduates can locate the other alumni members. Over 1,525 organizations at home and abroad employed graduates of the sIDB-BISEW IT Scholarship Programme.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>For placement assistance please contact:</p>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\"><strong>MD. HELALUR RAHMAN</strong><br />Program Officer (Placement) <br />IsDB-BISEW <br />Cell: <a href=\"tel:+8801670-462007\">+8801670-462007</a> <br />Phone: <a href=\"tel:+880%202 9183006\">+880 2 9183006</a> <br />Email: <a href=\"mailto:helal@idb-bisew.org\">helal@idb-bisew.org</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\"><strong>MD. SHARIFUL ISLAM</strong><br />Placement Officer<br />IsDB-BISEW IT Scholarship Project <br />Cell: <a href=\"tel:+880155-2450991\">+880155-2450991</a> <br />Email: <a href=\"mailto:sharif@idb-bisew.org\">sharif@idb-bisew.org</a></div>\r\n</div>', NULL, 'The most striking aspect of the project has been its outstanding placement record. Almost all graduates of the programme get placed in jobs right after completing their training. It currently maintains 92% of placement record. These employments take place in a wide variety of sectors and firms', NULL, 'publish', NULL, 'page', 'it-scholarship-programme', 'from_old', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 3, '2019-10-01 06:39:00', '2019-11-25 04:26:02');
