(64, 'Madrasah Education Programme Overview', NULL, 'madrasah-education-programme-overview', '<p>In Bangladesh, institutions of three streams &ndash; General, Madrasah and Vocational &ndash; delivering education in parallel, are engaged in the process of human resource development. Quite unfortunately, Madrasahs, occupying about one-fifth share in education delivery, are not ready to take part actively in the process of human resource development necessary both for its survival and national interest. Only a minor group of graduates is absorbed in some sorts of socio-religious services while majority are excluded from the mainstream socio-economic activities. That is why; IsDB-BISEW has taken an initiative to turn Madrasah students into a productive workforce. It has established 6 Madrasahs in different areas of Bangladesh under its pilot scheme and introduced Dakhil Vocational courses for the first time in Bangladesh.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1dnmaoe2114\">Rationale for Undertaking Madrasah Education Programme</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Establishing Madrasahs in some selected areas with adequate infrastructure and modern facilities</li>\r\n<li>Equipping Madrasah students with appropriate technical and vocational skills required in the job market</li>\r\n<li>Ensuring both higher education and employment opportunities for Madrasah students of Bangladesh</li>\r\n<li>Enhancing the social standing of graduates of the vocational programme</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1dnmaoe2115\">Areas for Financial Assistance</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Initial Setup\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\r\n<li>Construction of academic building and vocational workshops;</li>\r\n<li>Build-up of facilities with equipment, furniture and other supplies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Administration and Management\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\r\n<li>Recruiting qualified &amp; experienced management, teaching and support staffs for vocational and other training;</li>\r\n<li>Arranging continuous professional development for management, teachers and support staffs; and</li>\r\n<li>Providing guidance &amp; counseling and placement services.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Operational\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\r\n<li>Providing teaching-learning aids and resources for vocational trade; and</li>\r\n<li>Providing raw materials and auxiliary materials for vocational trade.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1dnmaoe2116\" class=\"heading3\">Specialty of IsDB-BISEW sponsored Madrasahs</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Modern and adequate infrastructure</li>\r\n<li>Special emphasis on quality vocational training</li>\r\n<li>Academically and professionally competent Instructors</li>\r\n<li>Availability of necessary tools and equipment for technical training</li>\r\n<li>Board-standard curriculum</li>\r\n<li>ICT facilities for the students</li>\r\n<li>Strong and sole supervision and monitoring by IsDB-BISEW</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1dnmaoe2117\" class=\"heading3\">Achievements of Madrasah Education Programme</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Pioneer in Bangladesh for introducing Dakhil Vocational Courses</li>\r\n<li>Running&nbsp; 3 different trades in Madrasahs</li>\r\n<li>451 students (upto 2014) successfully completed Dakhil (vocational) course</li>\r\n<li>Passing rate in Dakhil vocational exam:&nbsp; 96%</li>\r\n</ol>', NULL, 'In Bangladesh, institutions of three streams – General, Madrasah and Vocational – delivering education in parallel, are engaged in the process of human resource development. Quite unfortunately, Madrasahs, occupying about one-fifth share in education delivery, are not ready to take part actively in the process of human resource development necessary both for its survival and national interest.', NULL, 'publish', NULL, 'page', 'madrasah-education-programme', 'new', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '2019-10-21 05:39:00', '2019-11-03 06:44:35'),
(65, 'Four Year Diploma Scholarship Project objective', NULL, 'four-year-diploma-scholarship-project', '<p>The foremost objective of the projects is to empower each and every project beneficiary with right set of technical skills that ensure their sustainable occupations and future growth. The 4-Year Diploma Scholarship Project has commenced in the academic year July 2016.</p>\r\n<p>This scholarship for IDB-BISEW Dakhil (Vocational) Madrasah Project Graduates for 4-year Diploma Program under Government Polytechnic Institutes&nbsp; not only create opportunities for better livelihood of a beneficiary under the project, it would turn the underprivileged youth into skilled workforce employable in local and as well as overseas market.</p>', NULL, 'The 4-Year Diploma Scholarship Project has commenced in the academic year July 2016.', NULL, 'publish', NULL, 'page', 'four-year-diploma-scholarship', 'from_old', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '2019-10-21 06:04:19', '2019-10-21 06:06:59'),
(66, 'Madrasah Education Programme Selected Trades', NULL, 'madrasah-education-programme-selected-trades', '<div class=\"course-media d-flex\">\r\n<div class=\"course-media-picture\"><img src=\"/photos/shares/Module/Madrasah-Trade/01-general-electric-repair.jpg\" alt=\"General Electrical Works\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"course-media-content\">\r\n<h3>General Electrical Works</h3>\r\n<p>In addition to learning all the tricks of the electrical trade, you&rsquo;ll also learn how electrical repairs and installations vary between industrial, commercial, residential, and institutional applications..</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"course-media d-flex\">\r\n<div class=\"course-media-picture\"><img src=\"/photos/shares/Module/Madrasah-Trade/dress-making-and-trailoring.jpg\" alt=\"General Electrical Works\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"course-media-content\">\r\n<h3>Dress Making &amp; Tailoring</h3>\r\n<p>Dress making and tailoring is the selected trade of IsDB-BISEW Madrasah Project Trade. It can be help to acknowlede about the Dress making and tailoring.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"course-media d-flex\">\r\n<div class=\"course-media-picture\"><img src=\"/photos/shares/Module/Madrasah-Trade/welding-fabrication.jpg\" alt=\"General Electrical Works\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"course-media-content\">\r\n<h3>Welding Works</h3>\r\n<p>Welding &amp; Fabrication of metal refers to the building of metal structures. This is done via a variety of processes such as cutting, bending, profiling, welding and assembling..</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, 'IsDB-BISEW Madrasah Project Selected Trades', NULL, 'publish', NULL, 'page', 'four-year-diploma-scholarship', 'from_old', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '2019-10-21 06:30:23', '2019-11-03 06:39:54'),
